This paper discusses a technique for improving the programming of contingent logic in spreadsheets, which is a software engineering problem. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses the limitations of the technique, which could fall under cs.PL (Programming Languages) or cs.CY (Computational Complexity). The paper also mentions testing and auditing, which could fall under cs.DB (Databases) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
